description: This common Parvati purrs with a rating of 59, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 118, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Stringalong for East, Stringalong for South, and 8 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [118 Votes, Common]
